#. Max bytes: 251
msgctxt "Offset_0xBF850_Len_251"
msgid "The way to a cat's heart is through its stomach, so bring\r\nit some food! Once a cat has reached max affection, someone\r\nfrom the café will come to pick it up.\n\nBuy food at conveniences stores or the café\nand get out there to make some furry friends!"
msgstr ""

#. Max bytes: 268
msgctxt "Offset_0xBF950_Len_268"
msgid "餵貓吃飼料可以提昇親密度。\n當親密度達到MAX時，貓便會出現在貓咪咖啡廳內。\n\n在便利商店和貓咪咖啡廳中都有出售用來作為飼料的貓食罐頭。\n和街頭的貓拉近距離，讓貓咪咖啡廳中住滿這些嬌客吧！"
msgstr ""

